*PCFileName: "DTC4500e.ppd"
*ModelName: "DTC4500e"
*ShortNickName: "DTC4500e"
*NickName: "DTC4500e Card Printer"
*Manufacturer: "HID"
*Product: "(Card Printer)"
*cupsModelNumber: "5"
*LanguageVersion: English
*LanguageEncoding: ISOLatin1
*PSVersion: "(3010.000) 550"
*LanguageLevel: "2"
*ColorDevice: True
*DefaultColorSpace: RGB
*FileSystem: False
*Throughput: "3"
*LandscapeOrientation: Minus90
*TTRasterizer: Type42
*VariablePaperSize: False
*cupsVersion: 1.4
*cupsManualCopies: False
*cupsFilter: "application/vnd.cups-raster 50 rastertofargo-3.3.4"
*cupsLanguages: "de es fr it"

*% Changeable only through the command line or by application interfaces.
*Copies: 1
*MagTrack1: ""
*MagTrack2: ""
*MagTrack3: ""
*FPanelFrontFilename: ""
*FPanelBackFilename: ""
*FPanelInvertImage: ""
*ExclusionAreaFrontFilename: ""
*ExclusionAreaBackFilename: ""
*ExclusionKFrontFilename: ""
*ExclusionKBackFilename: ""

*XmlFilename: "/usr/share/fargo/DTC4500e/DTC4500e.xml"
*ColorProfileFilename: "/usr/share/cups/profiles/DTC4500eCLR.icm"
*ColorProfileFilenameL: "/usr/share/cups/profiles/DTC4500eCLR_L.icm"

*%==========================================================

*OpenGroup: CardOptions/Card

*OpenUI *PageSize/Card Size: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 10 AnySetup *PageSize
*DefaultPageSize: CR80
*PageSize CR80/CR80: "<</PageSize[152 242]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize CR79/CR79: "<</PageSize[148 238]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *PageSize

*OpenUI *CardThickness/Card Thickness: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 10 AnySetup *CardThickness
*DefaultCardThickness: 30
*CardThickness 10/10: "setpagedevice"
*CardThickness 20/20: "setpagedevice"
*CardThickness 30/30: "setpagedevice"
*CardThickness 40/40: "setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *CardThickness

*OpenUI *RotateFront180/Rotate Front 180 Degrees: Boolean
*OrderDependency: 10 AnySetup *RotateFront180
*DefaultRotateFront180: False
*RotateFront180 True/Yes: "setpagedevice"
*RotateFront180 False/No: "setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *RotateFront180

*OpenUI *RotateBack180/Rotate Back 180 Degrees: Boolean
*OrderDependency: 10 AnySetup *RotateBack180
*DefaultRotateBack180: False
*RotateBack180 True/Yes: "setpagedevice"
*RotateBack180 False/No: "setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *RotateBack180

*OpenUI *PageRegion: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 10 AnySetup *PageRegion
*DefaultPageRegion: CR80
*PageRegion CR80/CR80: "<</PageSize[152 242]/ImagingBBox null >>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion CR79/CR79: "<</PageSize[148 238]/ImagingBBox null >>setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *PageRegion

*DefaultImageableArea: CR80
*ImageableArea CR80/CR80: "0 0 152 242"
*ImageableArea CR79/CR79: "0 0 148 238"

*DefaultPaperDimension: CR80
*PaperDimension CR80/CR80: "152 242"
*PaperDimension CR79/CR79: "148 238"

*RequiresPageRegion All: True

*OpenUI *Resolution/Resolution: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 10 AnySetup *Resolution
*DefaultResolution: 300dpi
*Resolution 300dpi/300 DPI: "<</HWResolution[300 300]/cupsBitsPerColor 8/cupsRowCount 0/cupsRowFeed 0/cupsRowStep 0>>setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *Resolution

*OpenUI *InputHopper/Input Hopper Selection: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 10 AnySetup *InputHopper
*DefaultInputHopper: FirstAvailable
*InputHopper FirstAvailable/First Available: "setpagedevice"
*InputHopper Hopper1/Top: "setpagedevice"
*InputHopper Hopper2/Bottom: "setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *InputHopper

*CloseGroup: CardOptions

*%==========================================================

*OpenGroup: General/Print Options

*OpenUI *Ribbon/Ribbon Type: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 10 AnySetup *Ribbon
*DefaultRibbon: YMCKO
*Ribbon YMCKO/YMCKO: "setpagedevice"
*Ribbon YMCKO_Half/YMCKO Half Panel: "setpagedevice"
*Ribbon YMCKOK/YMCKOK: "setpagedevice"
*Ribbon YMCKK/YMCKK: "setpagedevice"
*Ribbon YMCFKO/YMCFKO: "setpagedevice"
*Ribbon YMCFKOK/YMCFKOK: "setpagedevice"
*Ribbon KStandard/Standard Resin: "setpagedevice"
*Ribbon KPremium/Premium Resin: "setpagedevice"
*Ribbon MonoColor/Colored Resin: "setpagedevice"
*Ribbon Metalic/Metallic Resin: "setpagedevice"
*Ribbon KO/Premium Resin/Overlay: "setpagedevice"
*Ribbon BO/Dye-Sub Black/Overlay: "setpagedevice"
*Ribbon None/None - Re-Writable: "setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *Ribbon

*OpenUI *PrintBothSides/Print Both Sides: Boolean
*OrderDependency: 10 AnySetup *PrintBothSides
*DefaultPrintBothSides: False
*PrintBothSides True/Yes: "setpagedevice"
*PrintBothSides False/No: "setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *PrintBothSides

*OpenUI *SplitRibbon/Split 1 Set of Ribbon Panels: Boolean
