*DefaultSplitRibbon: False
*SplitRibbon True/Yes: "setpagedevice"
*SplitRibbon False/No: "setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *SplitRibbon

*OpenUI *PrintBackOnFront/Print Back Image on Front of Card: Boolean
*OrderDependency: 10 AnySetup *PrintBackOnFront
*DefaultPrintBackOnFront: False
*PrintBackOnFront True/Yes: "setpagedevice"
*PrintBackOnFront False/No: "setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *PrintBackOnFront

*OpenUI *PrintBackOnly/Print Back Side Only: Boolean
*OrderDependency: 10 AnySetup *PrintBackOnly
*DefaultPrintBackOnly: False
*PrintBackOnly True/Yes: "setpagedevice"
*PrintBackOnly False/No: "setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *PrintBackOnly

*OpenUI *DisablePrinting/Disable Printing (Feed Card Only): Boolean
