*OpenUI *InvertFPanelImage/Invert F-Panel Image: Boolean
*OrderDependency: 10 AnySetup *InvertFPanelImage
*DefaultInvertFPanelImage: False
*InvertFPanelImage True/Yes: "setpagedevice"
*InvertFPanelImage False/No: "setpagedevice"
