*OpenUI *EncryptJobEnable/Encrypt Job Data: Boolean
*OrderDependency: 10 AnySetup *EncryptJobEnable
*DefaultEncryptJobEnable: False
*EncryptJobEnable True/Yes: "setpagedevice"
*EncryptJobEnable False/No: "setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *EncryptJobEnable

*CloseGroup: General

