*%==========================================================

*OpenGroup: OverlayOptions/Overlay Print Area Options

*OpenUI *PrintAreaFrontOption/Front Overlay/Print Area: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 10 AnySetup *PrintAreaFrontOption
*DefaultPrintAreaFrontOption: fullcard
*PrintAreaFrontOption fullcard/Full Card: "setpagedevice"
*% PrintAreaFrontOption defined/Defined Area(s): "setpagedevice"
*% PrintAreaFrontOption undefined/Undefined Area(s): "setpagedevice"
*PrintAreaFrontOption omitMagStripe/Omit Mag Stripe Area: "setpagedevice"
*PrintAreaFrontOption omitSmartChip/Omit Smart Chip Area: "setpagedevice"
*PrintAreaFrontOption omitSignature/Omit Signature Area: "setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *PrintAreaFrontOption

*% This attribute allows any value to be entered from the command line
*PrintAreaFrontOption: fullcard

*OpenUI *PrintAreaBackOption/Back Overlay/Print Area: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 10 AnySetup *PrintAreaBackOption
*DefaultPrintAreaBackOption: fullcard
*PrintAreaBackOption fullcard/Full Card: "setpagedevice"
*% PrintAreaBackOption defined/Defined Area(s): "setpagedevice"
*% PrintAreaBackOption undefined/Undefined Area(s): "setpagedevice"
*PrintAreaBackOption omitMagStripe/Omit Mag Stripe Area: "setpagedevice"
*PrintAreaBackOption omitSmartChip/Omit Smart Chip Area: "setpagedevice"
*PrintAreaBackOption omitSignature/Omit Signature Area: "setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *PrintAreaBackOption

*% This attribute allows any value to be entered from the command line
*PrintAreaBackOption: fullcard

*OpenUI *PrintAreaFrontApply/Front Apply Area(s): PickOne
*OrderDependency: 10 AnySetup *PrintAreaFrontApply
*DefaultPrintAreaFrontApply: PrintAndOverlay
*PrintAreaFrontApply PrintAndOverlay/Print and Overlay: "setpagedevice"
*PrintAreaFrontApply OverlayOnly/Overlay Only: "setpagedevice"
*PrintAreaFrontApply PrintOnly/Print Only (No Overlay): "setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *PrintAreaFrontApply

*OpenUI *PrintAreaBackApply/Back Apply Area(s): PickOne
*OrderDependency: 10 AnySetup *PrintAreaBackApply
*DefaultPrintAreaBackApply: PrintAndOverlay
*PrintAreaBackApply PrintAndOverlay/Print and Overlay: "setpagedevice"
*PrintAreaBackApply OverlayOnly/Overlay Only: "setpagedevice"
*PrintAreaBackApply PrintOnly/Print Only (No Overlay): "setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *PrintAreaBackApply

*OpenUI *VisualSecurityArea/Visual Security Solution: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 10 AnySetup *VisualSecurityArea
*DefaultVisualSecurityArea: None
*VisualSecurityArea None/No Visual Security: "setpagedevice"
*VisualSecurityArea UpperLeft/Upper Left: "setpagedevice"
*VisualSecurityArea UpperRight/Upper Right: "setpagedevice"
*VisualSecurityArea LowerLeft/Lower Left: "setpagedevice"
*VisualSecurityArea LowerRight/Lower Right: "setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *VisualSecurityArea

*OpenUI *VisualSecurityType/Visual Security Type: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 10 AnySetup *VisualSecurityType
*DefaultVisualSecurityType: VeriMark
*VisualSecurityType VeriMark/VeriMark: "setpagedevice"
*VisualSecurityType HoloMark/HoloMark: "setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *VisualSecurityType

*CloseGroup: OverlayOptions

*%==========================================================

*OpenGroup: KPanelOptions/K-Panel Options

*OpenUI *YMCunderKFront/Front YMC Under K: Boolean
*OrderDependency: 10 AnySetup *YMCunderKFront
*DefaultYMCunderKFront: False
*YMCunderKFront True/Yes: "setpagedevice"
*YMCunderKFront False/No: "setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *YMCunderKFront

*OpenUI *YMCunderKBack/Back YMC Under K: Boolean
*OrderDependency: 10 AnySetup *YMCunderKBack
*DefaultYMCunderKBack: False
*YMCunderKBack True/Yes: "setpagedevice"
*YMCunderKBack False/No: "setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *YMCunderKBack

*OpenUI *KPanelApplyFront/Front K-Panel Area: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 10 AnySetup *KPanelApplyFront
*DefaultKPanelApplyFront: none
