*OpenUI *Coercivity/Coercivity: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 20 AnySetup *Coercivity
*DefaultCoercivity: 2750
*Coercivity 4000/Super (4000 Oe): "setpagedevice"
*Coercivity 2750/High (2750 Oe): "setpagedevice"
*Coercivity 600/Medium (600 Oe): "setpagedevice"
*Coercivity 300/Low (300 Oe): "setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *Coercivity

*OpenUI *ShiftDataLeft/Shift Left Data: Boolean
*OrderDependency: 30 AnySetup *ShiftDataLeft
*DefaultShiftDataLeft: False
*ShiftDataLeft True/Yes: "setpagedevice"
*ShiftDataLeft False/No: "setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *ShiftDataLeft

*CloseGroup: MagneticEncoding

